===Adjective===

'''unkind'''

#Having no race or kindred; childless.
#Not kind; contrary to nature, or the law of kind or kindred; unnatural.
#Wanting in kindness, sympathy, benevolence, gratitude, or the like; cruel; harsh; unjust; ungrateful.

